name: ability
trans: The skill or power to do something.

name: accident
trans: Something bad that happens by mistake or without planning.

name: address
trans: The place where someone lives, including street name and number.

name: adventure
trans: An exciting experience or journey.

name: afternoon
trans: The time of day between noon and evening.

name: agree
trans: To have the same opinion as someone else; to say yes.

name: almost
trans: Nearly; very close to but not quite.

name: already
trans: By this time; before now.

name: among
trans: In the middle of a group; surrounded by.

name: answer
trans: A response to a question; what you say when someone asks something.

name: arrive
trans: To reach a place; to get to where you are going.

name: attention
trans: When you focus your mind on something and listen or watch carefully.

name: beautiful
trans: Very pretty or pleasing to look at.

name: believe
trans: To think something is true or real.

name: between
trans: In the middle of two things.

name: birthday
trans: The day you were born; celebrated each year.

name: brother
trans: A boy who has the same parents as you.

name: build
trans: To make or construct something by putting parts together.

name: busy
trans: Having a lot to do; not having free time.

name: captain
trans: The leader of a team or ship.

name: careful
trans: Taking care to avoid mistakes or danger; paying close attention.

name: carry
trans: To hold something and move it from one place to another.

name: center
trans: The middle point or part of something.

name: circle
trans: A round shape with no corners.

name: clothes
trans: Things you wear on your body like shirts, pants, and dresses.

name: common
trans: Happening often; usual or ordinary.

name: complete
trans: To finish something; having all parts.

name: country
trans: A large area of land with its own government and people.

name: cousin
trans: The child of your aunt or uncle.

name: create
trans: To make something new.

name: decide
trans: To make up your mind about something; to choose.

name: describe
trans: To tell or write about what something is like.

name: different
trans: Not the same; not alike.

name: discover
trans: To find something for the first time.

name: doctor
trans: A person who helps sick or hurt people get better.

name: during
trans: Throughout the time something is happening.

name: early
trans: Before the usual or expected time; near the beginning.

name: earth
trans: The planet we live on; also the soil or ground.

name: enjoy
trans: To like something and have fun doing it.

name: enough
trans: As much as you need; not too little.

name: example
trans: Something that shows what other similar things are like.

name: excited
trans: Feeling very happy and eager about something.

name: family
trans: People who are related to you, like parents, brothers, and sisters.

name: famous
trans: Known by many people; well-known.

name: favorite
trans: The one you like best of all.

name: finish
trans: To complete something; to reach the end.

name: follow
trans: To go behind someone or something; to come after.

name: forest
trans: A large area with many trees growing close together.

name: friend
trans: Someone you like and who likes you; a pal.

name: future
trans: The time that has not happened yet; what is to come.

name: garden
trans: A piece of ground where you grow flowers, fruits, or vegetables.

name: gentle
trans: Soft and kind; not rough or harsh.

name: giant
trans: Something or someone that is very, very big.

name: government
trans: The group of people who make rules and run a country.

name: group
trans: A number of people or things that are together.

name: guess
trans: To try to answer without knowing for sure.

name: happy
trans: Feeling joy and pleasure; not sad.

name: health
trans: The condition of your body; being well or sick.

name: holiday
trans: A special day when people don't work or go to school to celebrate.

name: honest
trans: Telling the truth; not lying.

name: important
trans: Something that matters a lot and is very special.

name: instead
trans: In place of something else.

name: invite
trans: To ask someone to come to an event or place.

name: journey
trans: A trip from one place to another.

name: jungle
trans: A thick forest in a hot place with many plants and wild animals.

name: kindness
trans: Being nice and caring toward others.

name: kitchen
trans: The room where food is cooked.

name: language
trans: The words people use to speak and write to each other.

name: learn
trans: To get new knowledge or skills by studying or practicing.

name: library
trans: A place where books are kept and you can borrow them.

name: listen
trans: To pay attention to sounds or what someone is saying.

name: market
trans: A place where people buy and sell food and other things.

name: middle
trans: The center point or part that is between two sides.

name: minute
trans: A short period of time; sixty seconds.

name: moment
trans: A very short period of time; an instant.

name: mountain
trans: A very tall, high piece of land that rises above the earth.

name: neighbor
trans: A person who lives near you.

name: nothing
trans: Not anything at all; zero things.

name: number
trans: A word or symbol that shows how many, like 1, 2, 3.

name: ocean
trans: A very large area of salty water.

name: office
trans: A room or building where people work at desks.

name: often
trans: Many times; frequently.

name: outside
trans: Not inside a building; in the open air.

name: parents
trans: Your mother and father.

name: people
trans: More than one person; human beings.

name: planet
trans: A large round object in space that moves around a star, like Earth.

name: present
trans: A gift; also means here or now.

name: pretty
trans: Nice to look at; beautiful.

name: promise
trans: To say you will definitely do something.

name: protect
trans: To keep someone or something safe from harm.

name: question
trans: Something you ask when you want to know information.

name: quietly
trans: In a way that makes little or no noise.

name: reason
trans: The explanation for why something happens or is done.

name: remember
trans: To think of something again; not to forget.

name: school
trans: A place where children go to learn.

name: season
trans: One of the four parts of the year: spring, summer, fall, or winter.

name: sister
trans: A girl who has the same parents as you.

name: snow
trans: White frozen water that falls from the sky in winter.

name: someone
trans: A person; somebody.

name: special
trans: Different from others in a good way; important.
